Not really, when we move selection color to `:after` element then we can create a sami-transparent overlay over the cells. This may cause some other issues (related to `position: relative` on `td.ck-editor__editable_selected`), but... we can try it ;-)', 'author': 'panr'}, {'body': '@panr Could you make a quick POC?', 'author': 'Reinmar'}, {'body': 'I checked and

